Lab Steps

1. Create a Resource Group

A Resource Group was created to logically organize Azure resources.

Applied Tag

| Tag Name    | Value         |
| ----------- | ------------- |
| Cost_Center | IT-Operations |

Purpose

The tag identifies which department or business unit owns the resources.



2. Enforce Tagging with Azure Policy

An Azure Policy was assigned to enforce mandatory tagging.

 Policy Used

Require a tag on resources

Configuration

Required Tag Name: Cost_Center

Behavior

If a resource is created without the required tag:

Resource creation is denied


Azure Policy Flow


User Creates Resource
        │
        ▼
Azure Policy Evaluation
        │
 ┌──────┴──────┐
 │             │
Compliant   Non-Compliant
 │             │
Allow       Deny Creation


3. Remediation Task

A remediation task was executed to apply inherited tags from the Resource Group level to previously created resources.

Result

Existing resources automatically inherited:

Cost_Center = IT-Operations



